{"tid":1242090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔好亂加密】- 只會益左3毛","createTime":"2019-06-19T02:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T19:38:59.000Z","uid":259820,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2a672c28f55fae75644681301cd8ae47dbe10e","tid":1242090,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:40:32.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論。<br />\n入得連登既3毛、分化撚一定有account，同埋已經開始狂出膠post粉飾太平。加密對佢無影響。<br />\n但一般網民/市民未必個個有account，佢地可能係cd-rom，但密切關注緊整體香港人有咩反應/下一步行動。好多中年、返工嘅人都有上連登。加密只會令佢地接收唔到第1手資訊，想幫手都唔知點幫好。<br />\n希望大家唔好郁啲就加密，612、616之所以咁多人響應，就係因為資訊充足，大家都知道發生緊咩事。<br />\n唔好喺呢個時候玩小圈子，只會益左想破壞行動嘅人﹗"},{"pid":"0f5f260507ee43b8e86b369175218317f0521dc9","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"691cdfb3b3ff5d68f247fa5d088b879da0e23da6","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d00ac5e1cda4b0322de7d1586468de3472522f1","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e344f05030ff0be74c88d42b9994b386e1f1ce08","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d4b7f547fa3a570f6310ccb9412569aff055ca9","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:53:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55450d760310c3412ed4caecd20cc0269db4a769","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:54:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"125a967bdaa66b8a81c71eccee3b9ef329702df7","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8b996e0f6355bea4f7ff3dc7849daf595924978","tid":1242090,"uid":261060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad7f